{"tid":565909,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港票房】《黑豹》破3千萬     《棟篤特工》破2千萬","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T15:00:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb5b2a042b136592123a9412376f65fe7c893af","tid":565909,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180219/large/1519034747_7f93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180219%2Flarge%2F1519034747_7f93.jpg&h=2a4ab89d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由美國40歲男星查特域克保斯曼（Chadwick Boseman）主演嘅Marvel新作《黑豹》（Black Panther），打破傳統係首部以黑人為主角嘅超級英雄電影，片中更以多達九成黑人演員參與演出，電影自周五於北美開畫單日收逾5.9億港元票房，首三天開出1.92億美元（14.9億港元）之驚人票房，加上周一係美國公眾假期，預計四天票房可累積達2.18億美元（17億港元），將超越《死侍》（Deadpool）打破2月份北美票房紀錄，更名列影史上首周最高票房總排名嘅第5位。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港方面截至今日黃昏，票房已衝破3,200萬港元，稱冠香港賀歲檔。至於海外票房，《黑豹》吸金1.69億美元（13.18億港元），全球總票房已達3.61億美元（28.15億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180219/57850868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850868&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=462b15f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850868&h=1294beb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180219/57850868</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180219/s00009/c7871a339616c3fcff909b697905259e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180219%2Fs00009%2Fc7871a339616c3fcff909b697905259e.jpg&h=1d98fad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由黃子華及佘詩曼主演的賀歲片《棟篤特工》，票房勢如破竹，由年卅晚（2月15日）上映，至昨日年初三僅僅4天，港澳兩地累積票房，已破2000萬，同時開創華語片3項紀錄，認真威水﹗<br />\n<br />\n子華神憑《棟篤特工》搣甩「票房毒藥」稱號，而據統計顯示，由他1993年第一部領銜主演的電影《情人知己》開始，25年來其領銜主演的電影總票房，約為 2717萬；而《棟篤特工》上映4日，票房已破 2000萬，超過子華神人生總票房的三分二。<br />\n<br />\n《棟篤特工》走勢凌厲，為向全港觀眾拜年及答謝支持，黃子華、佘詩曼、專家 Dickson、導演張家傑、監製陳穎倫聯同編劇等，昨晚開facebook live，舉行「今夜不防設之黃子華戒毒會 + 特工解答觀眾大會」，過程足足1.5小時，台前幕後邊傾偈邊答網民提問，邊飲酒邊開餐，十分開心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1519034749731&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1519034749731%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180219&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=7318483f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1519034749731%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180219&h=47ebce23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1519034749731&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180219</a>"},{"pid":"26d97f946ed18765ef2ea9607df3abed18b9e1b0","tid":565909,"uid":78622,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"黑豹笑片嚟 啲笑位仲多過劇情"},{"pid":"4f815e0899582beb83bebc9e564b4bc1e6804c4f","tid":565909,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"兩套垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港D票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a89cf46b911ab2be752360a210dd0a56158747","tid":565909,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"入場為左睇波多野咋"},{"pid":"2c37bb4b0704bbe9ea797fce9b91c4e621ab4ac6","tid":565909,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入場為左睇波多野咋</blockquote><br />\n波多野感謝祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}